{"tid":2379293,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【中印再戰】中印邊境又爆大亂鬥　目擊者：雙方均有人員受傷","createTime":"2021-01-25T06:39:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T14:06:31.000Z","uid":152636,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c9e93e33bfefb0525ae6b880a570138036d5f823","tid":2379293,"uid":152636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T06:39:41.000Z","msg":"中國和印度邊境又爆發士兵大亂鬥事件！根據法新社報導，此衝突發生在錫金省納庫拉地區，雙方均有人員受傷。<br />\n<br />\n法新社引述消息人士指出，此事發生在上周，地點就在錫金省納庫拉地區。印度媒體則引述印度軍官指出，中印兩邊軍隊均有人員受傷。<br />\n<br />\n此事距離上次中印在喜馬拉雅邊境的衝突事件僅不到半年。中印軍方則是在最新這起大亂鬥衝突後，周日（1/24）在「實際控制線」（Line of Actual Control）進行第9回談判協商。據《印度斯坦時報》報導，該談判持續15小時之久，但目前尚不清楚雙方是否達成具體協議。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210125/I4BP7WQ6TBFIRNZQVN47JHXEVI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210125%2FI4BP7WQ6TBFIRNZQVN47JHXEVI%2F&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABanyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=0fced014\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210125%2FI4BP7WQ6TBFIRNZQVN47JHXEVI%2F&h=bf698e1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210125/I4BP7WQ6TBFIRNZQVN47JHXEVI/</a>"},{"pid":"de81f27c43a0579aeae4d580e9c1d569b2aed462","tid":2379293,"uid":26770,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T06:45:28.000Z","msg":"印度加油,祝旗開得勝"},{"pid":"88adf0d4e43de7f84a058da22758400ce3812f5f","tid":2379293,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T06:46:15.000Z","msg":"打啦好嗎"},{"pid":"9f6837665cc6619964f4977fcf3a0dd0aaa2eec9","tid":2379293,"uid":151074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T06:50:35.000Z","msg":"幾驚某国放棄山地戰區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4767036c67b50ee5ebb0d8f1583